## 🎯 Project Overview

The **Urban Farming Platform** is a comprehensive backend system designed to bridge the gap between urban dwellers and local farming communities. This platform enables city residents to engage in sustainable agriculture through garden space rental, organic produce marketplace, plant tracking, and community knowledge sharing.

### Problem Statement

Urban residents face multiple challenges:
- ❌ Limited access to gardening spaces
- ❌ Difficulty finding organic, locally-grown produce
- ❌ Lack of knowledge about urban farming techniques
- ❌ No connection with local farmers
- ❌ No platform to track plant growth and health

### Our Solution

| Feature | Description | Benefit |
|---------|-------------|---------|
| 🏠 **Garden Space Rental** | Connect space owners with gardeners | Access to farming land |
| 🛒 **Organic Marketplace** | Direct farmer-to-consumer sales | Fresh organic produce |
| 🌱 **Plant Tracking** | Real-time growth monitoring | Better crop management |
| 💬 **Community Forum** | Share knowledge and tips | Learn from experts |
| ✅ **Sustainability Certification** | Verified organic products | Trust and quality |

### 👥 User Roles & Permissions

| Role | Icon | Permissions | Access Level |
|------|------|-------------|--------------|
| **Admin** | 👑 | Full platform control, user management, vendor approval, certification verification | All endpoints |
| **Vendor** | 🏪 | Manage farm spaces, list products, track orders, submit certifications | Vendor-specific endpoints |
| **Customer** | 👤 | Rent spaces, purchase products, track plants, community interaction | Customer-specific endpoints |

